      "message": "Personally I'd go with 'maxResults' everywhere.\n\nmaxResults is consistent with JPA/Hibernate naming conventions, where you have methods like query.setMaxResults.\n\n(FYI an alternate implementation here is to use query.setMaxResults(10) instead of explicitly adding LIMIT 10, but either is fine)",
